      "title": "Tablas del 2, 3 y 4",
      "html": "<!doctype html>\n<html lang=\"es\">\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"utf-8\" />\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width,initial-scale=1\" />\n  <title>Tablas del 2, 3 y 4</title>\n  <style>\n    body { font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, Segoe UI, Roboto, sans-serif; line-height: 1.5; padding: 1rem; }\n    h1, h2, h3 { margin: 0.2em 0; }\n    .badge { display:inline-block; font-size: 0.8rem; padding: 0.15rem 0.5rem; border-radius: 999px; background:#eef; margin-right: .4rem; }\n    .example, .task { border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 8px; padding: 0.8rem; margin: 0.8rem 0; }\n    .example h4, .task h4 { margin-top: 0; }\n    .note { font-size: .9rem; color:#333; background:#fafafa; padding:.6rem .8rem; border-left: 3px solid #ddd; border-radius:6px; }\n    .step { margin:.3rem 0; }\n    code.k { background:#f7f7f7; padding:.15rem .35rem; border-radius:4px; }\n    table.tabla { border-collapse: collapse; margin: 0.5rem 0; }\n    table.tabla td, table.tabla th { border: 1px solid #ccc; padding: 4px 10px; text-align: center; }\n    table.tabla th { background: #eef; }\n  </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n<h1>Tablas del 2, 3 y 4</h1>\n<div><span class=\"badge\">Eje</span> Tablas de multiplicar</div>\n\n<div class=\"example\">\n  <h4>Tabla del 2 — Los números pares</h4>\n  <table class=\"tabla\">\n    <tr><th>×</th><th>1</th><th>2</th><th>3</th><th>4</th><th>5</th><th>6</th><th>7</th><th>8</th><th>9</th><th>10</th></tr>\n    <tr><th>2</th><td>2</td><td>4</td><td>6</td><td>8</td><td>10</td><td>12</td><td>14</td><td>16</td><td>18</td><td>20</td></tr>\n  </table>\n  <p>Patrón: los resultados son siempre <strong>números pares</strong>. Cuenta de 2 en 2.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"example\">\n  <h4>Tabla del 3 — Cuenta de 3 en 3</h4>\n  <table class=\"tabla\">\n    <tr><th>×</th><th>1</th><th>2</th><th>3</th><th>4</th><th>5</th><th>6</th><th>7</th><th>8</th><th>9</th><th>10</th></tr>\n    <tr><th>3</th><td>3</td><td>6</td><td>9</td><td>12</td><td>15</td><td>18</td><td>21</td><td>24</td><td>27</td><td>30</td></tr>\n  </table>\n  <p>Patrón: cuenta de 3 en 3. Fíjate: <code class=\"k\">3, 6, 9, 12, 15...</code></p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"example\">\n  <h4>Tabla del 4 — El doble del doble</h4>\n  <table class=\"tabla\">\n    <tr><th>×</th><th>1</th><th>2</th><th>3</th><th>4</th><th>5</th><th>6</th><th>7</th><th>8</th><th>9</th><th>10</th></tr>\n    <tr><th>4</th><td>4</td><td>8</td><td>12</td><td>16</td><td>20</td><td>24</td><td>28</td><td>32</td><td>36</td><td>40</td></tr>\n  </table>\n  <p>Truco: multiplicar por 4 es lo mismo que multiplicar por 2 <strong>dos veces</strong>.</p>\n  <p>Ejemplo: <code class=\"k\">4 × 3 = ?</code> → primero <code class=\"k\">2 × 3 = 6</code>, luego <code class=\"k\">2 × 6 = 12</code></p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"note\">Practica contando de 2 en 2, de 3 en 3 y de 4 en 4 con tus dedos.</div>\n\n</body>\n</html>",
      "formulas": [],
      "assets": []
    },
    {
      "id": "stage-02",
      "order": 2,
      "title": "Tablas del 5 al 10",
      "html": "<!doctype html>\n<html lang=\"es\">\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"utf-8\" />\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width,initial-scale=1\" />\n  <title>Tablas del 5 al 10</title>\n  <style>\n    body { font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, Segoe UI, Roboto, sans-serif; line-height: 1.5; padding: 1rem; }\n    h1, h2, h3 { margin: 0.2em 0; }\n    .badge { display:inline-block; font-size: 0.8rem; padding: 0.15rem 0.5rem; border-radius: 999px; background:#eef; margin-right: .4rem; }\n    .example, .task { border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 8px; padding: 0.8rem; margin: 0.8rem 0; }\n    .example h4, .task h4 { margin-top: 0; }\n    .note { font-size: .9rem; color:#333; background:#fafafa; padding:.6rem .8rem; border-left: 3px solid #ddd; border-radius:6px; }\n    .step { margin:.3rem 0; }\n    code.k { background:#f7f7f7; padding:.15rem .35rem; border-radius:4px; }\n    table.tabla { border-collapse: collapse; margin: 0.5rem 0; }\n    table.tabla td, table.tabla th { border: 1px solid #ccc; padding: 4px 10px; text-align: center; }\n    table.tabla th { background: #eef; }\n  </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n<h2>Tablas del 5 al 10</h2>\n\n<div class=\"example\">\n  <h4>Tabla del 5 — Terminan en 0 o 5</h4>\n  <table class=\"tabla\">\n    <tr><th>×</th><th>1</th><th>2</th><th>3</th><th>4</th><th>5</th><th>6</th><th>7</th><th>8</th><th>9</th><th>10</th></tr>\n    <tr><th>5</th><td>5</td><td>10</td><td>15</td><td>20</td><td>25</td><td>30</td><td>35</td><td>40</td><td>45</td><td>50</td></tr>\n  </table>\n  <p>Patrón: todos los resultados terminan en <strong>0</strong> o en <strong>5</strong>.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"example\">\n  <h4>Tabla del 9 — El truco de los dígitos</h4>\n  <table class=\"tabla\">\n    <tr><th>×</th><th>1</th><th>2</th><th>3</th><th>4</th><th>5</th><th>6</th><th>7</th><th>8</th><th>9</th><th>10</th></tr>\n    <tr><th>9</th><td>9</td><td>18</td><td>27</td><td>36</td><td>45</td><td>54</td><td>63</td><td>72</td><td>81</td><td>90</td></tr>\n  </table>\n  <p>Patrón: la suma de los dígitos siempre da <strong>9</strong>.</p>\n  <p>Ejemplo: <code class=\"k\">9 × 4 = 36</code> → <code class=\"k\">3 + 6 = 9</code></p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"example\">\n  <h4>Tabla del 10 — Agrega un cero</h4>\n  <table class=\"tabla\">\n    <tr><th>×</th><th>1</th><th>2</th><th>3</th><th>4</th><th>5</th><th>6</th><th>7</th><th>8</th><th>9</th><th>10</th></tr>\n    <tr><th>10</th><td>10</td><td>20</td><td>30</td><td>40</td><td>50</td><td>60</td><td>70</td><td>80</td><td>90</td><td>100</td></tr>\n  </table>\n  <p>Patrón: solo agrega un <strong>0</strong> al número. ¡Es la tabla más fácil!</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"example\">\n  <h4>Tablas del 6, 7 y 8</h4>\n  <p>Estas tablas combinan lo que ya sabes:</p>\n  <div class=\"step\"><code class=\"k\">6 × 3 = ?</code> → Ya sabes <code class=\"k\">3 × 6 = 18</code>, ¡es lo mismo!</div>\n  <div class=\"step\"><code class=\"k\">7 × 4 = ?</code> → Ya sabes <code class=\"k\">4 × 7 = 28</code></div>\n  <div class=\"step\"><code class=\"k\">8 × 5 = ?</code> → Ya sabes <code class=\"k\">5 × 8 = 40</code></div>\n  <p>Si ya aprendiste las tablas del 2 al 5, ¡ya sabes gran parte de las tablas del 6 al 8!</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"note\">Truco: si olvidas una tabla, recuerda que puedes voltear la multiplicación. Por ejemplo, si no recuerdas 7 × 8, piensa en 8 × 7 = 56.</div>\n\n</body>\n</html>",
      "formulas": [],
      "assets": []
    },
    {
      "id": "stage-03",
      "order": 3,
      "title": "Quiz de tablas",
      "html": "<!doctype html>\n<html lang=\"es\">\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"utf-8\" />\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width,initial-scale=1\" />\n  <title>Quiz de tablas</title>\n  <style>\n    body { font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, Segoe UI, Roboto, sans-serif; line-height: 1.5; padding: 1rem; }\n    h1, h2, h3 { margin: 0.2em 0; }\n    .badge { display:inline-block; font-size: 0.8rem; padding: 0.15rem 0.5rem; border-radius: 999px; background:#eef; margin-right: .4rem; }\n    .example, .task { border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 8px; padding: 0.8rem; margin: 0.8rem 0; }\n    .example h4, .task h4 { margin-top: 0; }\n    .note { font-size: .9rem; color:#333; background:#fafafa; padding:.6rem .8rem; border-left: 3px solid #ddd; border-radius:6px; }\n    .step { margin:.3rem 0; }\n    code.k { background:#f7f7f7; padding:.15rem .35rem; border-radius:4px; }\n  </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n<h2>Quiz de tablas</h2>\n<p>¡Resuelve lo más rápido que puedas! Intenta no mirar las tablas.</p>\n\n<div class=\"task\">\n  <h4>Ronda 1 — Tablas fáciles</h4>\n  <ol>\n    <li><code class=\"k\">2 × 7 = ?</code></li>\n    <li><code class=\"k\">5 × 6 = ?</code></li>\n    <li><code class=\"k\">10 × 4 = ?</code></li>\n    <li><code class=\"k\">3 × 5 = ?</code></li>\n    <li><code class=\"k\">4 × 4 = ?</code></li>\n  </ol>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"task\">\n  <h4>Ronda 2 — Tablas medianas</h4>\n  <ol>\n    <li><code class=\"k\">6 × 4 = ?</code></li>\n    <li><code class=\"k\">7 × 3 = ?</code></li>\n    <li><code class=\"k\">8 × 5 = ?</code></li>\n    <li><code class=\"k\">9 × 2 = ?</code></li>\n    <li><code class=\"k\">3 × 8 = ?</code></li>\n  </ol>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"task\">\n  <h4>Ronda 3 — ¡Desafío!</h4>\n  <ol>\n    <li><code class=\"k\">7 × 8 = ?</code></li>\n    <li><code class=\"k\">9 × 6 = ?</code></li>\n    <li><code class=\"k\">6 × 7 = ?</code></li>\n    <li><code class=\"k\">8 × 9 = ?</code></li>\n    <li><code class=\"k\">7 × 7 = ?</code></li>\n  </ol>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"task\">\n  <h4>Ronda 4 — Completa el número que falta</h4>\n  <ol>\n    <li><code class=\"k\">? × 3 = 21</code></li>\n    <li><code class=\"k\">6 × ? = 48</code></li>\n    <li><code class=\"k\">? × 9 = 45</code></li>\n    <li><code class=\"k\">8 × ? = 32</code></li>\n  </ol>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"note\">Consejo: si te atoras en alguna, usa los patrones que aprendiste. Por ejemplo, para 9 × 6, recuerda que los dígitos suman 9: la respuesta es 54 (5 + 4 = 9).</div>\n\n</body>\n</html>",
